      "description": "Predicted pump pressure rise (ΔP) compared to experimental measurements across the full operating envelope. Uncertainty propagated from inlet flow rate measurement uncertainty and fluid property tolerances using Latin hypercube sampling. Structured UQ linked.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/lhs-pressure-rise-propagation"
    }
